<title>ALL HALL! IMMANUEL</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Lal Imanuel ka hun pak chau,
 Chawihat na cheng khuk sakin;
 Micheng cheng in hun chawian hen,
 Khawvel Aw hawih cheng tawh.
 Hukdampa Pathien chuh chawian in,
 Van in thil gihawih tin cheng suoh hen;
 A gi thangvel chuoi theilo in,
 Pak un, pak un, pak un pak un Imanuel.

[V2]
 Lal Imanuel, Imanuel (2)
 Lopina chawihatna leh Lal na;
 Chitna leh thilbawl theihna
 Kumsawt in Nanga hi hen;
 Lal Imanuel, Imanuel (2)
 Lalte lal leh Lal lopi,
 Pak un Imanuel.

[V3]
 2. Lal Imanuel ka hun pakchau,
 Tatsa te um kimvel in;
 Lei lalte'n a hun pakchau hi,
 Chawihatna la hawih tawh.
 Na Lalchutphah lopi kimvel ah,
 Na angsung thamuonna a chun;
 Pahchak na la chawl ta puona,
 Pak un, pak un, pak un, pak un Imanuel.

[V4]
 3. Lal Imanuel ka hun pakchau,
 Ka Hukdampa thokit chun;
 Melma dogal na zota a,
 Lalpa bangkim bawlthei.
 Gitloh thihna leh gawtmun na zo,
 Setan thuneih na cheng zo in;
 Na min kumsawt in lopi hen!
 Pak un, pak un, pak un, pak un Imanuel.</lyrics>
</song>